text: Uwe Billerbeck (born 28 May 1970) is a German gymnast. He competed in six events at the 1996 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1970 births Category:Living people Category:German male artistic gymnasts Category:Olympic gymnasts of Germany Category:Gymnasts at the 1996 Summer Olympics Category:People from Esslingen am Neckar
